---
title: User Lifecycle
---
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Registered: register(email, name)

    Registered --> Registered: updateProfile
    Registered --> LoggedIn: login

    LoggedIn --> LoggedIn: actions...
    LoggedIn --> Registered: logout
    LoggedIn --> Registered: session expires

    Registered --> [*]: delete

    note right of Registered
        Has profile
        No active session
        Can be invited to groups
    end note

    note right of LoggedIn
        Active session
        Can perform all actions
    end note
